msgid "üì¶ Applications"
msgstr "üì¶ Applications"

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/30.apps/index.mdx:11
#, no-wrap
msgid "One of the key feature of YunoHost is the ability to easily install applications which are then immediately usable. Example of applications include a blog system, a \"cloud\" (to host and sync files), a website, an RSS reader...\n"
msgstr "L'une des fonctionnalit√©s principales de YunoHost est la possibilit√© d'installer facilement des applications imm√©diatement utilisables. Pour donner des exemples d'application, il est possible d'installer un syst√®me de blog, un \"cloud\" (pour h√©berger et synchroniser des fichiers), un site web, un lecteur RSS...\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/30.apps/index.mdx:13
#, no-wrap
msgid "Applications can be installed and managed through the webadmin interface in <HighlightApplications/> or through commands of the `yunohost app` category.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/30.apps/index.mdx:15
#, no-wrap
msgid "<Figure caption=\"Apps list in the webadmin, with its Install button.\" src=\"/img/webadmin/apps_list.png\"/>\n"
msgstr "<Figure caption=\"Liste d'applications dans l'interface web d'administration, avec le bouton Installer.\" src=\"/img/webadmin/apps_list.png\"/>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/30.apps/index.mdx:17
#, no-wrap
msgid "The application catalog and its categories can be browsed directly from the webadmin by clicking on the <HighlightAppInstall/> button in the apps list, or from this documentation.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/admin/30.apps/index.mdx:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "<Button url=\"https://apps.yunohost.org/\" border=\"none\" color=\"black\" backgroundColor=\"orange\"><FAIcon icon='fa-cubes'/> Browse the application catalog <FAIcon icon='fa-arrow-right'/></Button>\n"
msgstr ""
"<Button url=\"https://apps.yunohost.org/\" border=\"none\" color=\"black\" "
"backgroundColor=\"orange\"><FAIcon icon='fa-cubes'/> Parcourir le catalogue "
"d'applications<FAIcon icon='fa-arrow-right'/></Button>\n"

#. type: Fenced div block (caution)
#: docs/admin/30.apps/index.mdx:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "Be careful and stay reasonable on the number of installed applications. Each additional installation increases the attack surface and the risk of failure. Ideally, if you want to test, do it with another instance for example in [a virtual machine](/admin/get_started/install_on/virtualbox).\n"
msgstr "Attention √† rester raisonnable sur le nombre d'applications install√©es. Chaque installation suppl√©mentaire augmente la surface d'attaque et les risques de panne. Id√©alement, si vous souhaitez faire des tests, faites-le avec une autre instance par exemple dans [une machine virtuelle](/admin/get_started/install_on/virtualbox).\n"

